{"tid":33221,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[星戰迷入］呢個角色係做乜嘢嘅？","createTime":"2016-12-10T16:10:36.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T08:42:07.000Z","uid":41237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"717e210ae7323da6f03161d8883039f6dd1fadd1","tid":33221,"uid":41237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T16:10:36.000Z","msg":"是咁的，最近會上星戰外傳啦，咁周圍都係宣傳<br />\n我就見到地鐵入邊有張咁嘅海報，令我有啲奇怪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/11/000433_f2156d4a94199ef9a4ed43755db3c9a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F11%2F000433_f2156d4a94199ef9a4ed43755db3c9a1.jpg&h=7b50bab5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁其實我就冇睇過星戰嘅，就有少少好奇<br />\n呢個角色到底係做咩嘅呢？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「深入敵軍基地通風報信」</span><br />\n嗱，我知入敵軍基地勘察、偵察係幫自己嗰邊吖<br />\n對自己嗰邊通風報信，都係幫自己嗰邊吖<br />\n<br />\n但係入敵人基地通風報信......即係反間諜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴絲可以解答下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66becd683eb3b2f21693fc1951f4f872d2f641cc","tid":33221,"uid":41237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T16:12:10.000Z","msg":"個排版好柒 大家唔好介意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa581b418046e8efb80bc9548bc8cd1b6adf4df8","tid":33221,"uid":56544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T21:21:12.000Z","msg":"擔當r2d2或者bb8既角色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68839a7b471abe812a72bbae94885bad425bd683","tid":33221,"uid":63863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T08:42:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>擔當r2d2或者bb8既角色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，緊被改左program,既c3po"}]}